&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; px=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; background-color:=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; line-height:=&quot;&quot; em=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;但是，如果我们只打算沿一个维度查看数据，那么将该维度作为具有最大变化的主成分可能会更好。 通过减少PC2，不会造成太大损失，因为它对数据集的变化贡献最小。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; pingfang=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; px=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; line-height:=&quot;&quot; em=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; box-sizing:=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.2898120672601385&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-w=&quot;1011&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb1LiatYc6o08Bc3JNK0O7vvRgC78Um21nP0KoZQBP7ksyORv4Y3xDKwC2qFVlVAqlZ9n2oibWQ4YibhA/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

